</div>

2
00:03.392 --> 00:10.702
<div class="key" data-key="2">
<p><span data-begin="00:03.392" data-end="00:03.392">የኒ፣ ሰሚር፣ ሄንን  ድሙን ኣብ ውሽጢ መሬት እዮም ዘለዉ።</span></p>
</div>

3
00:10.702 --> 00:13.082
<div class="key" data-key="3">
<p><span data-begin="00:10.702" data-end="00:10.702">ንኣሽቱ እዮም።</span></p>
</div>

4
00:13.082 --> 00:16.420
<div class="key" data-key="4">
<p><span data-begin="00:13.082" data-end="00:13.082">ኣብቲ ሓሰኻታት መሬት ዘዳለውዎ መንገዲ ይኸዱ ኣለዉ።</span></p>
</div>

5
00:16.420 --> 00:20.250
<div class="key" data-key="5">
<p><span data-begin="00:16.420" data-end="00:16.420">ሓደ ዝበልዕ ዘሎ ነገር ይሰምዑ ኣለዉ።</span></p>
</div>

6
00:20.250 --> 00:24.170
<div class="key" data-key="6">
<p><span data-begin="00:20.250" data-end="00:20.250">ቡናዊ ሕብሪ ዘለዎም ነገራት ይንቃሳቐሱ ኣለዉ።</span></p>
</div>

7
00:24.170 --> 00:29.050
<div class="key" data-key="7">
<p><span data-begin="00:24.170" data-end="00:24.170">-እዚ እቲ ሓሰኻ መሬት ድዩ? የኒ ሕሹኽ ትብል።</span></p>
</div>

8
00:29.050 --> 00:33.380
<div class="key" data-key="8">
<p><span data-begin="00:29.050" data-end="00:29.050">-እንታይ እዩ ዝገብር ዘሎ! ሰሚር ይሓትት።</span></p>
